Task Type | Loss Function | PyTorch Function | Use Case
Regression | MSE | nn.MSELoss() | Continuous output
Regression | MAE | nn.L1Loss() | Robust regression
Regression | Huber Loss | nn.SmoothL1Loss() | Outlier-sensitive regression
Binary Classification | Binary Cross-Entropy | nn.BCELoss() | Two-class classification
Binary Classification | BCE with Logits | nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss() | Better numerical stability
Multiclass Classification | Cross Entropy Loss | nn.CrossEntropyLoss() | Softmax + NLL combined
Multi-label | Multi-label BCE | nn.BCEWithLogitsLoss() | Multi-label problems
Segmentation | Dice / IoU / Focal | Custom / from libraries | Image segmentation, detection
